Come on, do you really believe this? First of all, contrary to popular belief there ARE spots where you will still find plenty of blues at 61, so don't make it sound like just dinging 61 makes the epic useless. Is the xp TONS better in PoP? Of course, but that would still leave a vast majority of the time (when you are everywhere else) that the epic is not only useful, but far superior. Why are you so adamant on trashing the epic? Even when you agree that the epic may outdamage you play it off like it's a small damage difference, not worth considering. I can see my epic proc 10 times a fight (and usually more) easily. If it hits for full, which I feel it probably does often, thats an extra 1430 in procs. Those procs add a ton of damage, and that's on top of the good possibility that it does more straight melee damage than the 61 air.<br>
