<br>
1.) Position of the pet must be the same for <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>all</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> pets. You will see huge difference dps-wise if you attack from the front, sides or back.<br>
<br>
2.) Run a long test: 3 to 4 minutes tests are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>useless</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. However you will get some good data after 30+ minutes.<br>
