<br>
================================<br>
=========== Fight #1 ==============<br>
================================<br>
<br>
Just melee,<br>
Epic: 47.07 DPS<br>
61 AIR: 61.05 DPS<br>
<br>
Melee + Proc,<br>
Epic: 80.44 DPS<br>
61 Air: 61.05 DPS <br>
<br>
Melee + Proc +DS,<br>
Epic: 85.51 DPS<br>
61 Air: 61.05 DPS <br>
<br>
Note:  I did not adjust for stun damage, not sure what it is exactly but the mob was stunned 2 times and this fight was 44 sec long.  Epic pet also stunned 2 times and that was not included either.<br>
<br>
================================<br>
=========== Fight #2 ==============<br>
================================<br>
<br>
Just melee,<br>
Epic: 48.91 DPS<br>
61 AIR: 49.32 DPS<br>
<br>
Melee + Proc,<br>
Epic: 98.06 DPS<br>
61 Air: 49.32 DPS <br>
<br>
Notes: Epic pet stunned 2 times this fight too, not counted in.  61 Air did not stun at all, but he was tanking.  This time.  Epic tanked the first time.<br>
<br>
